{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id747d68db-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"40732"},"text":"§ 40732.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Sale of firearms and supplies","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id747d68dc-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Affiliated Organizations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The corporation may sell, at fair market value, surplus caliber .22 rimfire rifles, caliber .30 surplus rifles, caliber .45 M1911/M1911A1 surplus pistols, and surplus pump action shotguns (except any shotgun that is a modular ancillary addition to a service rifle, or meets the definition of a “short-barreled shotgun” as that term is defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s921/a/6"},"text":"section 921(a)(6) of title 18","children":[],"tail":", United States Code), air rifles, caliber .22 and .30 ammunition, repair parts, and other supplies to organizations affiliated with the corporation that provide training in the use of firearms."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id747d68dd-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Gun Club Members","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68de-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The corporation may sell, at fair market value, surplus caliber .22 rimfire rifles, caliber .30 surplus rifles, caliber .45 M1911/M1911A1 surplus pistols, and surplus pump action shotguns (except any shotgun that is a modular ancillary addition to a service rifle, or meets the definition of a “short-barreled shotgun” as that term is defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s921/a/6"},"text":"section 921(a)(6) of title 18","children":[],"tail":", United States Code), ammunition, repair parts and other supplies necessary for target practice to a citizen of the United States who is legally of age and who is a member of a gun club affiliated with the corporation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68df-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Except as provided in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t36/s40733"},"text":"section 40733 of this title","children":[],"tail":", sales under this subsection are subject to applicable United States, State, and local law. In addition to any other requirement, the corporation shall establish procedures to obtain a criminal records check of the individual with United States Government and State law enforcement agencies."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e0-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Limitation on Sales","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e1-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" No person acquiring a firearm under this chapter may sell a repair part designed to convert a firearm to fire in a fully automatic mode.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e2-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The corporation may not sell any item to an individual who has been convicted of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e3-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a felony; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e4-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a violation of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s922"},"text":"section 922 of title 18","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e5-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7","identifier":"/us/usc/t36/s40732/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Sales by Other Persons","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"A person who receives a rifle or any ammunition, repair parts, or supplies under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t36/s40728B/c"},"text":"section 40728B(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" may sell, at fair market value, such rifle, ammunition, repair parts, or supplies. With respect to rifles other than caliber .22 rimfire and caliber .30 rifles, the seller shall obtain a license as a dealer in rifles and abide by all requirements imposed on persons licensed under chapter 44 of title 18, including maintaining acquisition and disposition records, and conducting background checks."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id747d68e6-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/225"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–225","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-08-12"},"text":"Aug. 12, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/1340"},"text":"112 Stat. 1340","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/dA/tX/s1087/a/2/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, div. A, title X, § 1087(a)(2)(C)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-11-25"},"text":"Nov. 25, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/1013"},"text":"129 Stat. 1013","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/328/dA/tX/s1096/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–328, div. A, title X, § 1096(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/2441"},"text":"130 Stat. 2441","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dA/tX/s1062/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. A, title X, § 1062(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1047"},"text":"139 Stat. 1047","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id747d68e7-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"},"text":"\n","childre